{"tid":164012,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果可以報復前人渣男朋友","createTime":"2017-03-20T11:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T14:04:06.000Z","uid":68675,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af10375778540f77ad87b8d05aaf6ab526ac5dbf","tid":164012,"uid":68675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:38:09.000Z","msg":"我上年11月比個人渣飛。<br />\n<br />\n我到分手個時候先知，佢係有左第二個女人！<br />\n<br />\n拍拖個時候，我都偷偷望到佢手機有個女仔揾佢！<br />\n<br />\n逢親我話借佢部手機睇下， 佢就會特別緊張，將部手機搶走！<br />\n<br />\n仲要，佢部電話有人打黎，佢專登唔聽電話，話冇人打電話黎！(佢教咗靜音模式，但係有來電顯示，我睇到)<br />\n<br />\n所以大家都要小心另一半咁樣嘅舉動！<br />\n<br />\n前嗰排，佢都話可能會同我復合。<br />\n但係，琴日就同我講以後都唔會再搵我！<br />\n然後刪除晒我啲聯絡方式，包括Facebook，IG，WhatsApp，Line。<br />\n<br />\n 於是我係WhatsApp send訊息畀佢，佢應該睇咗，但係冇覆我！<br />\n(因為我見到兩個灰色&radic; &radic;，但係就見唔到兩個藍色&radic; &radic;)<br />\n<br />\n我真係好傷心，拍左咁耐拖(兩年幾)，我估唔到佢係咁嘅人！偷食都算啦！仲要拋棄我，同小三一齊！<br />\n<br />\n 我依家真係好想報復佢！<br />\n<br />\n應該係話，究竟有咩方法我可以報復下？<br />\n我個心始終唔平衡！<br />\n<br />\n佢可以繼續拍拖同小三開心！<br />\n<br />\n而我變得孤獨寂寞一人！仲要個心好痛！<br />\n<br />\n我祝佢有一日都會孤獨終老！做得音質野多，生仔無屎忽！ 遲早一日佢都會比女仔玩返轉頭！"},{"pid":"5547ba1bbabdf78472d857c57d6de871c19a36bc","tid":164012,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:39:46.000Z","msg":"Wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仔死仔還在呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99588b6f53d8ffa93f4fcab5344417ab6b5af7c4","tid":164012,"uid":68675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:40:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仔死仔還在呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係丫！我宜家都係咁安慰自己內心！<br />\n始終覺得自己俾人玩左！"},{"pid":"872efb88ee470f3049ec9d533365c1f160274890","tid":164012,"uid":12363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"比我屌報復佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178abca5ecd9f921c6a8de998271785b9ba66901","tid":164012,"uid":92101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:41:39.000Z","msg":"有冇比人騙色先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇既就由佢啦"},{"pid":"a2793fe646064e2c8dce18acfa4fdb7434915fd1","tid":164012,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:41:59.000Z","msg":"明白放過你是放過自己"},{"pid":"1c59cf3d088eb8222d6f18061d79cd6d7636e378","tid":164012,"uid":31001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"同小三拍拖 告佢衰11囉<br />\nBtw 2年幾好少啫 搵過戶好人家係最好既報復"},{"pid":"8745a8abb1b94b68404416c7d7e8c6744bb93468","tid":164012,"uid":68675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇比人騙色先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇既就由佢啦</blockquote><br />\n都冇既！"},{"pid":"3860633925e0e4efd218fe7da92e50ba44b2350a","tid":164012,"uid":18139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:42:54.000Z","msg":"小你老母三咩<br />\n抵你俾你飛啦屌"},{"pid":"b37e9563c03d7da56020ec463f268daa9cb541b1","tid":164012,"uid":68675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:43:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同小三拍拖 告佢衰11囉<br />\nBtw 2年幾好少啫 搵過戶好人家係最好既報復</blockquote><br />\n我仲後生，仲可以慢慢搵嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2967994eff837ab442844b5572f02a63eb123f16","tid":164012,"uid":68675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小你老母三咩<br />\n抵你俾你飛啦屌</blockquote><br />\n咁個女仔叫咩好？<br />\n第三者？"},{"pid":"7007f280d68c03c8cf68322f00e709ec9f23ee87","tid":164012,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:45:12.000Z","msg":"做連登肉便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed03164f1ccbe436af398df50576617995a1591","tid":164012,"uid":31001,"li